RSG-Direct Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 5/3/2026

This Privacy Policy explains how RSG-Direct collects, uses, and stores user data.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Data Collected

RSG-Direct may collect and store the following data:
* Discord User ID
* Discord Username
* Steam Account ID or profile link
* Verification status (e.g. ownership of Ready or Not)
* Generated verification keywords (temporary)
* Server-related activity data

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. How Data is Used

Data is used to:
* Verify ownership of the account
* Link Discord accounts to Steam accounts
* Prevent duplicate account linking
* Assist staff with moderation and verification
* Maintain server integrity and security

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. Data Storage

* Data is stored in a secure database
* Access is restricted to authorized staff only
* We take reasonable steps to protect stored data

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or share your data with third parties.

Data may only be accessed:
* By authorized server staff for moderation purposes
* When required by law (if applicable)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

5. Data Retention

* Data is stored as long as necessary for verification and moderation purposes
* Users may request data removal (see Section 6)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

6. User Rights

You have the right to:
* Request access to your stored data
* Request correction of inaccurate data
* Request deletion of your data

To do so, contact bot staff or administrators.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

7. Security

While we take reasonable precautions, no system is completely secure. Use of the bot is at your own risk.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

8. Changes to Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time. Continued use of RSG-Direct indicates acceptance of any changes.
